2006-05-23  Steven Price  <ecrips@users.sourceforge.net>

	* hdrecover.cpp (main): Split out sector fixing code to
	correctsector. Now reads BLOCKSIZE (10k) bytes at a time until a
	read error is encountered and then drops to reading one sector at
	a time --- which is MUCH faster!

